    <item>
      <title>丹麦总理无视诺和诺德的经济扩张风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/novo-nordisk-growth-isn-t-big-risk-to-denmark-s-economy-pm-frederiksen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森表示，她对该国的优秀企业“感到非常自豪”，并否认了制药巨头诺和诺德公司的任何下滑会破坏经济稳定的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/novo-nordisk-growth-isn-t-big-risk-to-denmark-s-economy-pm-frederiksen-says</guid>
