    <item>
      <title>首尔警告将对朝鲜垃圾气球采取军事行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/seoul-warns-of-military-actions-over-north-korea-trash-balloons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国警告称，如果朝鲜继续越过边境投放更多垃圾气球，韩国可能会采取军事行动。自五月朝鲜开始投放垃圾气球以来，这是韩国罕见的直接报复威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/seoul-warns-of-military-actions-over-north-korea-trash-balloons</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 04:23:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理考虑对富裕和大型企业征税以解决债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了弥补法国庞大的预算赤字并安抚国际投资者，法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 决定对富人和大公司征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨在德国州选举中再次败给极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-escapes-another-defeat-to-far-right-in-german-state-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党击败了极右翼的德国选择党，看上去将在东部勃兰登堡州继续执政，从而使总理和他的政党避免再次遭遇令人尴尬的选举挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-escapes-another-defeat-to-far-right-in-german-state-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 20:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼总统就任，国际货币基金组织担忧加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡新任左翼总统在周一的选举中以压倒性优势获胜后宣誓就职，赶走了该国精英阶层。选民指责这些精英阶层因国际货币基金组织救助计划相关的严厉紧缩措施导致国家破产并给经济带来巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 14:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非团结党在市场乐观情绪中迎来成立 100 天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/south-african-unity-government-at-100-days-amid-market-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西里尔·拉马福萨重掌政权并领导的非洲人国民大会同意与反对党组成执政联盟已经 100 天了。尽管联盟被认为提振了市场情绪，但可以说，拉马福萨早先的改革才是当前乐观情绪的推动因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/south-african-unity-government-at-100-days-amid-market-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 11:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
